f Product. What You'll Be Doing (i.e., Job Duties) In this role, you will be leading a team of PM's focused on building foundational products in Data, Trust & Safety domains that are easily extensible in terms of enabling new innovative products for consumer and institutional segments & also launching in different geographies. We are looking for driven, self motivated product leader with a deep understanding & experience in data & fraud/risk management for payments, someone who has a proven track record of building & launching product solutions for fraud prevention in the areas on stolen financials, ATO, identity management & building platforms to handle fraud and processes for obtaining fraud signals. The scope of responsibilities will include building solutions, strategies & data models for analysis of ATO, stolen financials and end to end related work flow. Additional responsibilities include: Spearhead strategy & vision to create, build & deploy innovative data & ML product solutions for new & existing products Manage a team of PM's across Data, Trust & Safety teams. Manage & prioritize the roadmap for Data and Trust/Safety domains. Build relationships with stakeholders and teams to help influence & drive successful outcomes. Challenge existing status quo and push for new, effective & efficient solutions. Work with the engineering and data sciences teams to execute, deploy, test and iterate products and solutions that drive successful outcomes for the customer and the business. What We Look For In You (ie. Job Requirements) 10 yrs or more experience working in Payments/Fintech companies & launching successful products at scale. Deep focus on understanding customer problems and coming up with hypothesis based solutions. Bachelors in data science, MS preferred. Seasoned leader with Data Products, Product Analytics, ML modeling background. Ability to build strategy, prioritize & deploy new innovative solutions with focus. Self driven leader with excellent communication skills who can influence cross functional teams to rapidly launch products. Have a proven iterative test & learn mindset to launching products. Experience interfacing with exec leadership. Email me jobs like this About Coinbase Coinbase is the world\u2019s most popular way to buy and sell bitcoin and ethereum. Founded in June of 2012, Coinbase is a digital currency wallet and platform where merchants and consumers can transact with new digital currencies like bitcoin and ethereum. We're based in San Francisco, California. Bitcoin is the world's most widely used alternative currency with a total market cap of approximately $10 billion. The bitcoin network is made up of thousands of computers run by individuals all over the world. Â  Our mission is to create an open financial system for the world An open financial system is one that is not controlled by any one country or company (just like the internet did for distributing information). We think this is the highest leverage way to bring about more economic freedom, innovation, efficiency, and equality of opportunity in the world. We have a ten year plan to get there. Imagine if every payment in the world was as fast, cheap, and global as sending an email. Imagine if anyone who had an idea for a product could have customers all over the world from day one. Imagine if anyone with a smartphone had access to the the same financial services we enjoy in the developed world. An open financial system can be a great equalizer and lift billions out of poverty while accelerating the pace of innovation around the world. This is the best way we know to change the world. Company Profile Apply Now Share this job: Home Contact About Us Terms & Conditions Employer Post a Job Search Resumes Sign in Job Seeker Find Jobs Create Resume Sign in Facebook Twitter Google Plus LinkedIn Â© 2008-2020Â Blocktribe TM"
